<p>Is it possible to achieve sth like this using PHP and Google Docs (or probably newer Google Drive) API:</p>  <ul> <li>user logs into my application (not using Google account) </li> <li>user inside of my application (best option) opens Google Documents editor</li> <li>user creates a template document containing text, images etc. Template contains also some custom tags like {{name}} or {{surname}}</li> <li>user saves the template</li> <li>user picks for example 500 records with names from my application and my application generates zip with 500 PDFs inside. Every PDF is converted by Google template-document (tags like {{name}} replaced with values from records)</li> </ul>  <p>Thanks</p>